        <item>
            <title>生成式 AI 试衫突破想像　DETERMINANT 推出「61 Shirts For Everywhere」企划</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/determinant-shirts-for-everywhere/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=determinant-shirts-for-everywhere</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/determinant-shirts-for-everywhere/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 03:23:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[恤衫]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[时装]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生成式 AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[衬衫]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1216354</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>生成式 AI 技术的应用范畴相当广泛，往往可以带来我们意想不到的结果。最近有本地衬衫品牌就推出了<a href="https://bit.ly/47MGCMI">「61 Shirts For Everywhere」企划</a>，提供全新 AI 试衫服务，配合其高科技功能衬衫产品。<br /><span id="more-1216354"></span></p><h2>以生成式 AI 技术突破想像</h2><p>传统以来衬衫都给人一种只在办公室或者正式场合穿着的印象，今次<a href="https://bit.ly/4b9dwKi">本地品牌 DETERMINANT</a> 推出的「61 Shirts For Everywhere」企划，就希望可以打破这个传统形象，重新塑造衬衫的形象，在不同的场合其实也能够透过合适的衬衫表现自己时尚的一面。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1216734 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_essential-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_essential-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_essential.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_essential-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1216735 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_heatguard-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_heatguard-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_heatguard.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_heatguard-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>DETERMINANT 特别选用了近来相当热门的 Midjourney 图像生成 AI 模型，结合旗下各种衬衫的特色，让模型生成出虚拟模特儿试衫的图片，透过超越人类想像力的新科技，探索更多不同的可能性，也让人重新思考不同的穿搭可以如何配合自己。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1216736 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_instantco-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_instantco-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_instantco.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_instantco-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1216737 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_supreme_g-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_supreme_g-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_supreme_g.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/61s_igfeed_supreme_g-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>衬衫产品同样高科技</h2><p>除了应用新科技来重新想像衬衫穿搭，<a href="https://bit.ly/3vIJHjQ">DETERMINANT 的衬衫</a>本身也并非以前的麻烦衣物，采用了不同的新物料来提升其功能性，穿着起来舒适之余也方便保持清洁感。</p><h3>Wrinkle-Free 免烫抗皱系列</h3><p>衬衫给人一种麻烦形象的元凶，往往是每次洗衫后的烫衫环节。而免烫抗皱系列衬衫就采用了「Cross-Linking」技术，为纤维创造稳定性，实现 DP 3.5 抗皱等级；配合缝接位置的嵌条，令肩膊线、腰线等容易皱褶的位置于洗衫后仍然保持笔直俐落，减省烫衫的烦恼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217104 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt_1-694x254.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="254" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt_1-694x254.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt_1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>VISDRY<sup>TM</sup> 系列</h3><p>衬衫在炎炎夏日要如何保持清洁，避免水渍、汗渍和雨水沾湿，一向是个挑战。有见及此，这 VISDRY<sup>TM</sup> 系列就使用专利技术，加入跣水外层，避免水渍形成，此外内层亲水材质也可以快速吸收和分散湿气，不留下污渍和异味，避免黏笠感，可以时刻保持干爽整洁。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217105 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt02-694x227.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="227" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt02-694x227.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>InstantCool 系列</h3><p>另一款针对炎夏开发的衬衫是 InstantCool 系列，采用独特的棉质和天然 TENCEL 纤维混合制成，带来轻量清新感觉。此外配合了矽油材质帮助散热，或以薄荷精华提供凉快感及抗菌效果，同时达到 DP 3.5 抗皱等级，容易打理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217106 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt03-694x228.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="228" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt03-694x228.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt03.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>Supreme 系列</h3><p>DETERMINANT 的旗舰衬衫 Supreme 系列则进一步采用更高级的材质，包括比一般棉花更柔韧耐用的 YL39 棉花品种、加入丝绸混纺的布料 ，或以纱支数高达 100 支双的缇花布制成， 抗皱等级达 DP 4.0 ，触感舒适柔软之余更进一步提升抗皱功能性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217107 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt04-694x255.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="255" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt04-694x255.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt04.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>HeatGuard 系列</h3><p>要在冬天保暖，一般可能会想像需要穿着臃肿的御寒衣物，不过其实新的布料技术已经可以同时兼顾时尚风格和保暖效能。HeatGuard 系列就采用了火山岩人造丝线材质，透过火山岩的微孔结构锁住热力，达到保暖效果。此外特别加入远红外线（FIR）涂层，让衬衫能够吸收太阳电磁辐射并提高保温效率，据实验室测试显示可使温度提升 1.4°C，在寒冷天气下也能保持自在。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217108 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt05-694x255.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="255" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt05-694x255.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/shirt05.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Unwire.hk 读者专享优惠</h2><p>为了庆祝<a href="https://bit.ly/47MGCMI">「61 Shirts For Everywhere」企划</a>的推出，今次 DETERMINANT 特别为 Unwire.hk 读者准备了专享优惠，只要注册新会员，并在 Unwire.hk 的 Facebook 或 Instagram 贴文上回答简单的问题，就会选出最有创意的 61 个答案，得奖者可以 HK$98 特惠价选购免烫抗皱系列衬衫一件（原价 $398），也可以支付差价选购其他心水衬衫，有兴趣的朋友就不要错过优惠活动啦！<br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】GPT Store 正式开放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一张相帮你谂食谱</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/07/meta-imagine/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Meta 生成式 AI 绘图　多种画风选择 + 「手指」表现不俗</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/25/john-lee-cares-about-ai-data-safety/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">议员：滥用 AI 技术影响国家安全　李家超：不应由科技带著法律走</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/determinant-shirts-for-everywhere/life-tech/">生成式 AI 试衫突破想像　DETERMINANT 推出「61 Shirts For Everywhere」企划</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
